#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/help/jsonrpc_jsp.java:471
msgid "Authentication"
msgstr "인증"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/help/jsonrpc_jsp.java:473
msgid ""
"All API operations (except for authentication itself) require a valid "
"authentication token. To obtain a token, you must first authenticate with "
"your configured password:"
msgstr ""
"모든 API 작업(인증 자체 제외)에는 유효한 인증 토큰이 필요합니다. 토큰을 얻으려면 먼저 구성된 비밀번호로 인증해야 합니다:"

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/help/jsonrpc_jsp.java:475
msgid ""
"The returned token must be included in either the 'Token' parameter or as an"
" 'X-Auth-Token' HTTP header in all subsequent API calls."
msgstr ""
"반환된 토큰은 모든 후속 API 호출에서 'Token' 매개변수 또는 'X-Auth-Token' HTTP 헤더에 포함되어야 합니다."

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/help/jsonrpc_jsp.java:477
msgid ""
"API Version: 1. Clients must specify API version 1 in authentication "
"requests for compatibility."
msgstr "API 버전: 1. 클라이언트는 호환성을 위해 인증 요청에서 API 버전 1을 지정해야 합니다."

#: /tmp/build-i2p/apps/routerconsole/java/build/../../jsp/WEB-INF/classes/net/i2p/router/web/jsp/help/jsonrpc_jsp.java:479
msgid "API Methods"
msgstr "API 메서드"

